COMMMANDS TO RUN:
1. Temrminal 1 - start controller
cd ~/pox
source pox-env/bin/activate
sudo pkill -f pox
python pox.py openflow.discovery misc.link_failure

2. Terminal 2 - start mininet
cd ~/Link-Failure-Recovery-SDN
sudo mn -c
sudo mn --custom topology/custom_topo.py --topo custom --controller=remote

3. Show topology- custom topology with redundant path
mininet> net

4. Connectivity test
mininet> pingall

SEE RTT(LATENCY) before failure
mininet> h1 ping -c 5 h2

5. Flow table before failure
mininet> dpctl dump-flows

6. Throughtout(Bandwidth -iperf)
server start:
mininet> h2 iperf -s &
Client start:
mininet> h1 iperf -c 10.0.0.2

7. Simulate Link failure 
mininet> link s1 s2 down
SEE RTT(LATENCY) after failure
mininet> h1 ping -c 5 h2

8. TESTS AFTER FAILURE
mininet> pingall
mininet> h2 iperf -s &
mininet> h1 iperf -c 10.0.0.2
mininet> dpctl dump-flows
mininet> net

mininet> exit
Ctrl + C
